title: 2021 CFB Pick Em Week Zero
description:
Forget all the skell slander and attempted squeeze outs because we are BACK. El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are all together in studio after a long offseason. Big Cat (who has read "Art of the Deal") plays agent to help Rico negotiate a new contract with Dave and everyone has picks for week zero of the college football season.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
